            "text": "<p>Every seam is sealed with waterproof tape to prevent water from entering through stitching holes — a professional hard-shell standard for reliable storm protection.</p><p>OmniShell uses <strong>PFAS-free seam tapes and treatments</strong>, delivering strong waterproof performance without harming the environment.</p>",
            "target_tab": "description",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 32
